## Reconstructed baseline snapshot for the strongest known 5-sleeve crypto portfolio.
## Purpose:
## - rebuild a deployable/env-driven approximation of `portfolio_20260325_172613_new_5strat_final`
## - use the exact symbol participation observed in that strongest run
## - create a clean comparison and eventual rollback candidate instead of relying on memory

